HEADWORD: Bronchophony
<hw>Bron*choph"o*ny</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <?/
windpipe + <?/ sound.]</ety> <def>A modification of the voice sounds, by
